<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="502" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="18.[785,1380,1696,2124]" lastBlockId="18.[165,1377,2129,3464]" pageId="18" pageNumber="502">
After some taxonomic changes, Cabrera in 1958 assigned 
<taxonomicName box="[1042,1185,1893,1926]" class="Mammalia" family="Phyllostomidae" genus="Gardnerycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="502" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="crenulatum">crenulatum</taxonomicName>
to the genus 
<taxonomicName box="[788,882,1933,1966]" class="Mammalia" family="Phyllostomidae" genus="Mimon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="502" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Mimon</taxonomicName>
, in the subgenus 
<taxonomicName box="[1153,1304,1933,1966]" class="Mammalia" family="Phyllostomidae" genus="Anthorhina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="502" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Anthorhina</taxonomicName>
. Several taxa have been associated with 
<taxonomicName class="Mammalia" family="Phyllostomidae" genus="Gardnerycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="502" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="crenulatum">crenulatum</taxonomicName>
, obscuring its relationships. Based on phylogenetic analysis, N. Hurtado and V. Pacheco in 2014 reassigned 
<taxonomicName box="[1235,1379,2091,2124]" class="Mammalia" family="Phyllostomidae" genus="Gardnerycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="502" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="crenulatum">crenulatum</taxonomicName>
to the new genus 
<taxonomicName box="[423,604,2129,2162]" class="Mammalia" family="Phyllostomidae" genus="Gardnerycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="18" pageNumber="502" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Gardnerycteris</taxonomicName>
. Three subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
